---
import { whatsappUrl } from '../../data/site';

const reveal = 'opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition duration-700 ease-out';
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="grid min-h-[calc(100vh-6rem)] gap-10 px-1 py-10 sm:px-3 sm:py-14 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(420px,612px)] lg:items-center lg:gap-14 lg:py-16"
>
  <div data-reveal class={`${reveal} flex flex-col items-start`}>
    <span class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#fff2f3] px-4 py-2 text-[0.72rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-nasa-accent">
      <svg class="size-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M3 12h4l2-5 4 10 2-5h6" />
        <path d="M18 5v4M16 7h4" />
      </svg>
      Excelencia automotriz
    </span>

    <h1 class="m-0 text-[clamp(3.4rem,8vw,5.8rem)] leading-[0.9] tracking-[-0.08em] text-nasa-accent">
      <span class="block font-display font-bold uppercase">NASA</span>
      <span class="mt-2 block text-[clamp(2.6rem,6vw,4.2rem)] font-light italic text-slate-500">Auto Lab</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-7 max-w-[34rem] text-lg leading-[1.75] text-slate-500 sm:text-[1.55rem] sm:leading-[1.7]">
      Ingenieria de excelencia y rigor profesional, con un equipo en constante formacion para proteger y optimizar tu vehiculo con integridad, garantizando un rendimiento de alta calidad.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href={whatsappUrl}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-nasa-accent px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-[0_16px_28px_rgba(239,12,24,0.26)] transition hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Agendar Cita
      </a>
      <a
        href="#servicios"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-nasa-text transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50"
      >
        Nuestros Servicios
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div data-reveal style="transition-delay:120ms" class={`${reveal} relative`}>
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_28px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.18)]">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1619642751034-765dfdf7c58e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80"
        alt="Mecanico trabajando sobre el motor de un vehiculo"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
        class="h-full min-h-[24rem] w-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[-1.1rem] left-[-1.1rem] grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/90 p-3 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.12)]">
      {Array.from({ length: 12 }).map(() => <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-[#f6c7cb]"></span>)}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
